Class Transporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • others.Resource
      • human.HumanResource
        • human.Transporter

  • public class Transporter
extends HumanResource
    Transporters are part of the human resources. They transport a patient from a consultation to any health service.

      • transportation

        public void transportation(Patient patient)
        This simulates the transportation of a patient. This transporters's state is set to transporting, the patient's state is set transported. The room in which the patient was picked up is set to empty.
        Parameters:
        patient - The patient waiting for transportation

      • endOfTransportation

        public void endOfTransportation(Patient patient)
        This simulates the drop off of the patient by this transporter. The patient is added to the wainting queue corresponding to its destination, it is set to waitinForExamination and his location is updated. The patient is unassigned to this Transporter
        Parameters:
        patient - The patient being transported
